{"tid":44363,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓貓打交問題","createTime":"2016-12-18T08:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T12:10:29.000Z","uid":38899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fada52ef5bf9e3d65552748251fc1f4c4521351e","tid":44363,"uid":38899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:22:02.000Z","msg":"小弟最近屋企黎左隻街貓乸，咁佢之後生左三隻公貓仔。<br />\n<br />\n佢地二個月大咁上下我攞左一隻貓仔比朋友，而其餘三仔乸就住係我到。<br />\n如是者過左一個月，D貓都相安無事，但係前日我個朋友要去旅行，就比番隻貓我照顧。<br />\n點知一番日果日D貓就炒大鑊，個呀媽就係咁惡隻貓仔同打佢。而家就演變到其他貓仔都好神經質，郁D就(胡) 同埋打其他貓(呀媽連以前一齊係我到住果D貓都照) <br />\n(暫時放左呀媽去後園)<br />\n有冇巴打知道點解決?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee62052098572ecb422f3bbcca10365d5c20fa4","tid":44363,"uid":38899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:23:41.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d96bba3a992dfe5dfb49e322d6ff50774ac102b","tid":44363,"uid":38899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:27:36.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc21c704bba073f3ccd111c99cd863cd22cf5597","tid":44363,"uid":5443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"你要將俾咗朋友隻貓困籠"},{"pid":"d349b196a5a87234c897c77629ec222b59ce2c7d","tid":44363,"uid":38899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:32:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要將俾咗朋友隻貓困籠</blockquote><br />\n無籠點攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1374620b4abb0f576bbc8311c6b8be753b88a549","tid":44363,"uid":22481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:34:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你要將俾咗朋友隻貓困籠</blockquote><br />\n無籠點攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無籠仲有得攪，無腦真係無得攪"},{"pid":"4c508da49f515a69e999578f14a8b2f80